GW's canon is that Skaven are all male. There are female "Broodmothers," but they are sessile, possibly not even sapient, and never seen on the surface. If we can generalize from the males as a starting point, male Skaven in the aggregate tend strongly to be stunted, skinny, weak, stupid, illiterate or nearly so, and have a switch in their heads that periodically toggles back and forth between "abject comic-opera coward" and "cackling fanatic eager to die for the cause of his people's god." They are a comedy relief faction like the Orks, but even uglier and less sympathetic. There have been attempts to create cute, attractive, and sympathetic Skaven "adventure girls":

https://archiveofourown.org/works/44565586

It is, in my opinion, spotty, and it doesn't always gel, but I give the author points for trying.

I have said before that Skaven are just Burmecian punk rockers, and Burmecians are just Skaven preppies. If we imagine it this way, then maybe we can have Skaven women who aren't repulsive, who could be normal and desirable if they just had an education and a good bath. Maybe Evil Rat Queen is part Skaven on her father's side and the stress about the deep dark family secret is what makes her act like a cunt so much.
